## File layout per block

```
blocks/m3d-<name>/
  m3d-<name>.js      # decorate(block) function, Three.js scene
  m3d-<name>.css     # .m3d-<name> { position:relative; width:100% }
  _m3d-<name>.json   # XWalk model (<=4 fields, definitions+models+filters)
```

