## AEM model constraints (enforced)
- Max 4 fields per model (`xwalk/max-cells` lint rule). OVERRIDE if needed!
- Or alternately use the controls in the main UE dropdown of component
- Also use subcomponents when it makes sense
- All JSON files must follow `definitions` + `models` + `filters` schema.
- fj.mcp MUST be used for all `_*.json` files.

